1. Correct creation of the "SecureFiles" directory in the home directory (1 point)
2. Proper creation of the three required text files "file1.txt," "file2.txt," and "file3.txt" inside the "SecureFiles" directory (1 point)
3. Appropriate permission settings for "file1.txt": readable, writable, and executable by the owner, and readable by others (1 point)
4. Proper permission settings for "file2.txt": readable and writable by the owner only (1 point)
5. Correct permission settings for "file3.txt": readable, writable, and executable by the owner and the group (1 point)